rows.label: qst101411_msg201

rows.label: qst101411_msg301
rows.name: おぉ！危険生物の巨大エネミー（仮） を倒してくれたのですね！

rows.label: qst101411_msg302
rows.name: 大変感謝致します！

rows.label: qst101411_msg0001
rows.name:
You've returned! What news
of the research party?

rows.label: qst101411_msg0002
rows.name:
A Rampaging Sauros?! I never knew
creatures like that lived in Gula...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0003
rows.name: So everyone's... I see...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0004
rows.name:
Would you mind telling me exactly
where you found them all?

rows.label: qst101411_msg0005
rows.name: Thank you...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0006
rows.name:
At the very least, I expect the
Volff won't be too keen to return
to where their comrades fell.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0007
rows.name:
And since you've taken care of
the Rampaging Sauros, the threat
to the area should have passed.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0008
rows.name:
I think I'll go and pay my
respects to my fallen friends.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0009
rows.name:
That, and I'd like to have
something I could pass on
to their families...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0010
rows.name:
Thank you once again
for your cooperation!

rows.label: qst101411_msg0101
rows.name:
You've returned! What news
of the research party?

rows.label: qst101411_msg0102
rows.name:
A Rampaging Sauros?! I never knew
creatures like that lived in Gula...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0103
rows.name: So everyone's... I see...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0104
rows.name:
I'd... I'd like to go and
pay my respects, but...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0105
rows.name:
With that thing around, it might
be too dangerous for me...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0106
rows.name: A Rampaging Sauros... Hmm...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0107
rows.name:
There's a scholar by the name of
Tishek in the Beraf Industry Ward of
the Superbian capital, Alba Margen.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0108
rows.name:
I vaguely remember him publishing a
paper on the Rampaging Sauros...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0109
rows.name:
Maybe he'd know a good
way to dispatch one?

rows.label: qst101411_msg0110
rows.name:
I'm sorry, I know that's
not a lot to go on...

rows.label: qst101411_msg0111
rows.name:
But I appreciate your
continued help, friend.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0201
rows.name:
Go to Alba Margen in Superbia
and find Tishek in the Beraf
Industry Ward, please.

rows.label: qst101411_msg0202
rows.name:
You may be able to learn
a good way to put down
that Rampaging Sauros...
